{
  "stem": "4764.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, I remember the-- being very scared, and this is why I don't like that platform.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the next thing is-- is-- is this horse drawn carriage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Budapest in 1943 was a fantastic-looking town, the first city I'd-- apart from Czechoslovakia, which wasn't all that great.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But this was beautiful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know, have you ever been to-- it's fantastic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It really is a very beautiful city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was in '43, anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's got the river and it had streets and houses, and-- and there was no one-- there was no-- it wasn't occupied yet.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was free.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't stay there very long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We stayed-- Budapest is divided into two, Buda on one side of the Danube and Pest on the other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think we stayed in Pest, in a block of units, for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we went to a little village outside of the main city, a wine-growing area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That's where I-- I remember a lot about because I-- we spent a long-- quite a long time there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it must have been summertime, again, because-- by this time, I didn't have to wear the three jumpers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was-- it was quite warm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a warm day, so it must have been summer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, it was summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the first city I have ever seen, which was-- the first metropolis, actually, the first free city where actually there was no-- there was no soldiers on the road.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no guns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- apart from police, I suppose there were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it looked-- you know, it just looked like something that I had never seen, so it was just fantastic.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And actually going in this horse drawn carriage, you know, was just amazing, along the cobblestone streets.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
